Requirements:
For Monolithic:deploy the wordpress and mysql on 1EC2 Instanace
1)launch the instance with AMI as UBUNTU and instance as t2.micro
2)then install the mysql and wordpress on the server
3)choose instance type as t2.micro
For Microservices:deploy the wordpress and mysql on two different EC2 Instanace

Resources Used:refer some help of youtube,AWS documentation,and my notes

